<p><strong>AC</strong> 20, touch 10, flat-footed 20 (+9 armor, +1 natural)<br/><strong>hp</strong> 71 (8d8+32)<br/><strong>Fort</strong> +8, <strong>Ref</strong> +2, <strong>Will</strong> +8; +2 resistance vs. good<br/><strong>Defensive Abilities</strong> orc ferocity; <strong>Immune</strong> fire (96 points)</p>
